{"title":"念奴娇　悼李志民将军（图片）","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":11,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"念奴娇　悼李志民将军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘志坚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将星又落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冻云翻骤添多少寒意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幽燕歌悲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霜叶飞铺满李公归路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哀鸿齐天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"素帐垂地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌溢千掬泪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜阑惊梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却见当年英姿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾燃井冈篝火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又照延河月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西进挥戈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东渡舞戟，　〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感一世功丰德昭勋著。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神州腾飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方遂平生志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘愿成泥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九泉来日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邀公再续青史。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕李志民将军解放前夕曾率部西进，解放甘肃、宁夏，朝鲜战争爆发，又挥师入朝作战，痛歼美李，振我国威军威。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}